The part number you want is 071-251-053C.

Leistritz and Ernst (German) have stopped making this mullfer. Maybe BD has some left. You can find Dansk (Denmark) and ANSA (Italy) at various vendors.

http://wolfsburgwest.com/cart/DetailsList.cfm?ID=071251053C

